list_page_teaser: I often get my friends to answer the questionnaire so I can learn more about them and draw their image.  View this gallery to see the resultant images, and learn about them as well.
description_html:
These are some images of my friends in Denver, drawn with the latest version of the Groja © program.

I will be adding more friends to this page, as I gather their scores and get their ok to add them, so check back soon!

image_list.title: Chantee
image_list.gallery_page_teaser: Click on the image to learn more!
image_list.explain_dom: The Red in Chantee's spiritual portrait represents her making emotional decisions.
image_list.explain_aux: The Blue in Chantee's spiritual portrait represents her openness and idealism.

image_list.title: V.M.
image_list.gallery_page_teaser: Click on the image to learn more!
image_list.explain_dom: The Blue in VM's spiritual portrait represents her openness and idealism.  In Extraverts, the dominant function is directed outwardly, and spiritual portraits use a long vertical line to represent this.
image_list.explain_aux: The Red in VM's spiritual portrait represents her preference for making emotional decisions.  In Extraverts, the auxiliary function is directed inwardly and is less evident than the dominant function.
